<br>
I looked into satillite.  2 way satillite, which is the best, would provide me with pings at around 800ms.  Playing EQ with your ping in the yellow or red is BAD.<br>
<br>
I am on a 56k modem (thoroughputs are more like 23k) I experience the yellow/red pings during raids.....and I'll tell you this.  I get to watch most of our members run back to our camp site.....swinging at the air like they are fighting.  I get to see the mob stand there, with no hps.....and no one attacking it.  I get to see myself hitting the mob for damage.....up to 60 seconds after he has died.....and have on many occasions died to enrage......60 seconds after he died.<br>
<br>
Satillite and EQ = BAD <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4347"><IMG src="http://www.nwlink.com/~bstevens/Rogues/images/viscer1.jpg" border=0></a><br>
